        p1: "South Tyrol is one of Italy's regions with the highest concentration of artisanal and productive excellence. Yet, digitally, many of these businesses remain invisible or inadequately represented.",
        p2: "The tourist looking for an agriturismo, the client wanting to contact a local supplier, the professional looking for an office in the area: everyone goes to Google first. If you're not there, with something that actually works, you don't exist for them.",
